## Conventions

- `FakeListLLM` / `FakeChatModel` for unit tests (never call real API)
- One test per chain behavior
- Fixtures for mock LLM and chains
- Test output parsers separately
- `MagicMock` for `with_structured_output` when needed
- Integration tests separated (marked with `@pytest.mark.integration`)
